enum affymetrix_calvin_parameter::ParameterNameValueDefaultRequiredType::ParameterValueType

The type of value.

Enumerator:
NoParameterType 
IntegerParameterType  Not set.
FloatParameterType  Integer stored in the MIME value.
TextParameterType  Floating point stored in the MIME value.
DateParameterType  Text stored in the MIME value.
TimeParameterType  Date stored in the MIME value as text.
DateTimeParameterType  Time stored in the MIME value as text.
ControlSingleParameterType  DateTime stored in the MIME value as text.
ControlMultiParameterType  Controlled multi selection stored in the controlMulti list.
